Transitions.ErrorBack: Go back to the previous action
Transitions.FeatureDescription: Transitions is a report showing the things your visitors did directly before and after viewing a given page. This page explains how to access, understand, and use the powerful "Transitions" report.
Transitions.AvailableInOtherReports: Did you know? Transitions are also available as a row action in the following reports:
Transitions.AvailableInOtherReports2: Launch transitions by clicking their icon (%s) after hovering a row in any of these reports.
Transitions.NoDataForActionDetails: Either the action had no pageviews during the period, or it is invalid.
Transitions.PeriodNotAllowedDetails: Try selecting a period with fewer days for this feature.
Transitions.PluginDescription: Reports previous and following actions for each page URL in a new "Transitions" report, available in the "Actions" reports via a new icon.
Transitions.ShareOfAllPageviews: This page had %1$s pageviews (%2$s of all pageviews)
Transitions.XOfAllPageviews: %s of all views of this page
